savedSearches.displayName: OM - R2 - OIC - Health - Error Percentage

uiConfig.queryString: 'Log Source' = 'OCI Integration Activity Stream Logs' | link Instance | stats unique('OCI Resource Name') as 'OCI Resource Name', unique(Integration) as Integration, unique(OICStatus) as Status | eval Failed = if(Status = literal(Failed), 1, 0) | eventstats distinctcount(Instance) as TotalExec, sum(Failed) as ErrorExec | eval ErrorRate = unit(ErrorExec / TotalExec * 100, pct) | timestats name = 'Error Rate' avg(ErrorRate) as 'Avg. Error Rate' by Integration | fields -Status, -Failed, -'Start Time', -'End Time', -Instance, -Count | dedup Integration

customActionsDefinitions.customActionTarget:
'Log Source' = 'OCI Integration Activity Stream Logs' and Identifier != null 
| link includenulls = true 'OPC Request ID',
   'Transaction ID',
   Action 
| rename 'Group Duration' as 'Transaction Time' 
| sequence name = Milestones [ Action != null and 'Action Type' != null and 'Event ID' != null ]{1,} 
   select Action,
   'Action Type',
   'Event ID',
   Integration 
| stats latest(Integration) as Integration,
   unique('OIC Project') as 'Project Name',
   distinctcount(Identifier) as Integrations,
   unique(Entity) as Entity,
   unique(Instance) as Instance 
| addfields [ Key = ordernumber 
    | eventstats latest(Value) as PO by 'OPC Request ID',
       'Transaction ID',
       Action ] 
| eventstats unique(PO) as PO by 'Transaction ID' 
| where PO in $PO
| timestats avg('Transaction Time') as 'Time Taken' by PO,
   Integration

uiConfig.queryString: 'Log Source' = 'OCI Integration Activity Stream Logs' and Identifier != null | link includenulls = true 'OPC Request ID', 'Transaction ID', Action | rename 'Group Duration' as 'Transaction Time' | sequence name = Milestones [ Action != null and 'Action Type' != null and 'Event ID' != null ]{1,} select Action, 'Action Type', 'Event ID', Integration | stats latest(Integration) as Integration, unique('OIC Project') as 'Project Name', distinctcount(Identifier) as Integrations, unique(Entity) as Entity, unique(Instance) as Instance, unique(OICStatus) as Status | addfields [ Key = ordernumber | eventstats latest(Value) as PO1 by 'OPC Request ID', 'Transaction ID', Action ] | eventstats unique(PO1) as PO by 'Transaction ID' | eventstats distinctcount(Integration) as Integrations, distinctcount(PO1) as POs | addfields [ * | where Status = failed and PO != null | eventstats distinctcount(PO) as 'Failed POs' ] | addfields [ * | where Status = failed | createtable name = 'Failed PO Details' select PO, Integration, Action, 'OPC Request ID' ] | eventstats ifnull(max('Failed POs'), 0) as 'Failed POs' | classify correlate = -*, PO, 'Project Name' 'Start Time', Action, Integration, 'Transaction Time' as 'Transaction Execution Time' | classify correlate = -*, 'Project Name', 'Transaction ID' 'Start Time', PO, Action, Integration, 'Transaction Time' as 'PO Execution Time' | fields -PO, -PO1 | fields target = ui -'OPC Request ID', -Entity, -Instance, -Integrations, -POs, -'Failed POs'

'Log Source' = 'OCI Integration Activity Stream Logs' | eval 'Purchase Order' = if(Key = ordernumber, Value, null) | link 'Purchase Order' | sequence name = 'Sequence of Events' [ Integration != null ]{1,} select Integration | fields -Count

'Log Source' = 'OCI Integration Activity Stream Logs' and [ Key like '*' and Value like '*' | distinct 'Transaction ID' ] | link 'Transaction ID', Key, Value, Integration | eventstats latest('OIC Project') as 'Project Name', earliest('Start Time') as 'Started at', latest('End Time') as 'Last Action Time' | createtable name = 'Request Summary' select 'Transaction ID', 'Project Name', 'Started at', literal(exception) as 'Selected Action', Integration as 'Integration Name', Key as 'Tracking Field', Value as 'Tracking Field Value'

uiConfig.queryString: 'Log Source' = 'Oracle Fusion Apps: Enterprise Scheduler Service' | link 'Request ID' | stats unique(Application) as Application, avg(ElapsedTime) as E, unique('Instance Parent Id') as 'Parent ID', unique('Job Display Name') as Job, unique('Parent Request ID') as 'Parent Req ID', unique('Product Name') as Product, unique('Product Family') as 'Product Family', latest('State Description') as Status, unique(Submitter) as Submitter | eval 'Time Taken' = unit(E, ms) | eval U = url('https://oracle.com', View) | eventstats distinctcount('Request ID') as Requests, avg(E) as AE, latest(U) as Details by Product, Job, Status | eval 'Average Time Taken' = unit(AE, ms) | createtable name = 'Job Summary' select Product, 'Product Family', Job, Status, Requests, 'Average Time Taken', Details | classify 'Start Time', Job, 'Time Taken', Product, 'Product Family', Status as 'ESS Jobs Analysis' | fields -E, -AE

LINK_SEARCH_SETTINGS.linkSummaryInput: <title-text>OIC Service Instances</title-text> <title-text>Projects</title-text> <title-text>Total Integrations</title-text> <title-text>Transactions</title-text> <title-text>Integration Instances</title-text>

uiConfig.queryString: 'Log Source' = 'OCI Integration Activity Stream Logs' and 'Transaction ID' != null | link 'OCI Resource Name' | addfields [ 'Project ID' = null and Identifier != null | stats distinctcount(Identifier) as 'standalone-integs' ] | eventstats distinctcount('OCI Resource Name') as 'OIC Service Instances', distinctcount('Project ID') as 'Unique Projects', distinctcount('OPC Request ID') as 'Unique Transactions', distinctcount(Identifier) as 'Unique Integrations', distinctcount(Instance) as 'Instance Execs', sum('standalone-integs') as 'Standalone Integrations' | fields -Count, -'standalone-integs', -'Start Time', -'End Time'

'Log Source' = 'OCI Integration Activity Stream Logs' | link 'OPC Request ID' | eventstats distinctcount(Instance) as Instances, distinctcount(Identifier) as Integrations, distinctcount('User ID') as Users, distinctcount('OCI Resource Name') as Environments | stats unique(Instance) as Instance, unique(Identifier) as 'Integration Id', unique(Endpoint) as Endpoint, unique('User ID') as User, unique('OCI Resource Name') as 'OCI Env', unique(Integration) as Integration, unique(Action) as Action | extract field = 'Integration Id' '(?P<Integration>[^!]*)' | rename 'Group Duration' as 'Time Taken' | classify correlate = -*, Action 'Start Time', 'Integration Id', Integration, 'Time Taken' as 'Flows Execution Time Analysis' | fields target = ui -Instances, -Integrations, -Users, -Environments
